- cs.LT (Automata and Formal Languages) is another possible category as the paper deals with equivalences on processes, which can be modeled as automata or formal languages.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper discusses techniques for verifying the correctness of software systems.
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is another possible category as the paper deals with equivalences on processes, which can be modeled as formal languages and automata.
